  (str content) (str `[Amendment of Act 2 of 1934.] Rep. by the Repealing and Amending Act, 1960 (58 of 1960), s. 2
and the First Schedule (w.e.f. 26-12-1960).`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00007_195523_1517807318520&sectionId=35236&sectionno=52&orderno=64&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00007_195523_1517807318520)
